snippet.title: New Johnny Depp And Amber Heard Documentary To Release The Dark Truth...
snippet.description:
The story of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's relationship is very much a saga. A saga of two people who fell madly in love with one another on the set of a movie, and then became so and towards one another (allegedly...) that a massive divorce happened. End of story? Not so much. Because Amber Heard accused Johnny Depp of, he fought back against that claim, and the next nearly 5 years have been wrapped up in court cases and events that seemingly won't end. It's something that the movies would perfectly break down...and we're going to get that, kind of. We'll break it down for you.

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC76r9K-_Knc7d38c9uKRwaw?sub_confirmation=1 

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the documentary to be about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Can you believe that this is honestly what is going to happen? Are you shocked that it's going to occur before the final chapter in the story (presumably) is even written? Do you see this as a money grab for Discovery+ versus an honest look at the truth? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
